data.description: Looking for a lake home that has it all?  This 3-bedroom 1 1/2 bath home has been recently renovated with no expense spared.  Renovations include new paint, light fixtures, water heater, microwave, wood blinds, security system, and kitchen wiring.  When entering this home from the kitchen or den you will notice all tile flooring.  The kitchen also has granite counters and stainless-steel appliances.  The kitchen cabinets have been painted and have all new hardware.  The hallway leaving the kitchen and den leads to 3 bedrooms with the master at the end.  The master bedroom has double doors that open to a large, screened porch overlooking the lake and saltwater pool with a waterfall.  There is also a large deck for you to enjoy with family and friends.  Down below, you have a 2-car garage for storing your water toys.  The yard has a sprinkler system, and the boathouse has a lift set up for a 24-foot pontoon boat or could be configured to fit your boat.  Call your favorite agent for a showing.
